    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>From the Java documentation:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thrown to indicate that the requested operation is not supported.</p>\n<p>― <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/lang/UnsupportedOperationException.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Example usage:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>throw new UnsupportedOperationException(&quot;Feature incomplete. Contact assistance.&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 12120,
      "reputation" : 18965,
      "user_id" : 23704,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 66,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/87299cb8f7091eb5d271ce82b4303710?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Guillaume",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/23704/guillaume"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 16,
    "last_activity_date" : 1647793070,
    "last_edit_date" : 1647793070,
    "creation_date" : 1241610198,
    "answer_id" : 829187,
    "question_id" : 829136,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you want more granularity and better description, you could use <code>NotImplementedException</code> from <a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/javadocs/api-2.6/org/apache/commons/lang/NotImplementedException.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>commons-lang</code></a></p>\n<p>Warning: Available before versions 2.6 and after versions 3.2 only.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
